@baseUrl = https://localhost:7153

### GET todos los pedidos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Accept: application/json

###

### GET pedido por ID (devuelve 404 en skeleton)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
Accept: application/json

###

### POST crear pedido
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "a4b5c6d7-e8f9-0123-4567-89abcdef0123",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

###

### Health check (registrado por ServiceDefaults)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### OpenAPI spec (solo en Development)
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json
